In battle, it
flaps its wings
at high speed to release highly
toxic dust into
the air.
It releases a stench from its red\nantenna to repel enemies. It\ngrows by molting repeatedly.

Usually found in
power plants.
Easily mistaken for a POKé BALL,
they have zapped
many people.

A POKéMON that
has been admired
since the past for its beauty.
It runs agilely
as if on wings
